The brunette.

11
00:04:27,345 --> 00:04:28,573
Lori.

12
00:04:31,516 --> 00:04:34,485
I can't believe
you're jealous of a dream.

13
00:04:35,187 --> 00:04:38,054
- Who is she?
- Nobody.

14
00:04:38,123 --> 00:04:40,353
"Nobody"? What's her name?

15
00:04:40,425 --> 00:04:41,858
I don't know.

16
00:04:43,161 --> 00:04:44,958
- Tell me!
- I don't know!

17
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:47,328
You better tell me!

18
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:51,165
It's not funny, Doug.
You dream about her every night.

19
00:04:51,236 --> 00:04:53,932
And I'm always back
