20
00:04:54,005 --> 00:04:55,438
Let me go!

21
00:04:57,976 --> 00:05:00,103
Come on, baby.

22
00:05:00,178 --> 00:05:03,204
You know you're the girl
of my dreams.

23
00:05:03,281 --> 00:05:04,976
You mean it?

24
00:05:06,084 --> 00:05:08,018
You know I do.

25
00:05:17,462 --> 00:05:20,397
I'll give you
something to dream about.

26
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:30,508
The chairman defended the attack,
saying that space-based weapons...

27
