saying that space-based weapons...

28
00:05:34,179 --> 00:05:38,275
are our only defense against the
southern block's numerical superiority.

29
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:40,784
And more violence
last night on Mars...

30
00:05:40,852 --> 00:05:43,184
where terrorists
demanding independence...

31
00:05:43,255 --> 00:05:46,713
