of terbinium ore.

32
00:05:51,663 --> 00:05:53,893
Kuato and his so-called
freedom brigade...

33
00:05:53,965 --> 00:05:55,990
claimed credit
for this latest bombing,

34
00:05:56,067 --> 00:05:59,332
which attempted to reopen
the sealed-off Pyramid Mines.

35
00:06:02,841 --> 00:06:06,299
Mars military restored order
with minimal use of force...

36
00:06:06,378 --> 00:06:10,178
and all damage to the strategic facility
was repaired within hours.

37
00:06:10,248 --> 00:06:11,738
No cameras!

38
00:06:11,816 --> 00:06:15,912
With one mine already closed,
Mars administrator Vilos Cohaagen...

39
00:06:15,987 --> 00:06:18,080
vowed that troops
would be used if necessary...

40
00:06:18,156 --> 00:06:21,990
to keep production
at full capacity.

41
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:25,496
No wonder you're having nightmares.
You're always watching the news.

42
00:06:29,801 --> 00:06:32,065
- Lori.
- Doug?

43
00:06:32,137 --> 00:06:35,504
- Let's do it.
- Do what?

44
00:06:35,573 --> 00:06:37,006
Move to Mars.

45
00:06:38,109 --> 00:06:41,510
Why do you have to spoil
a perfectly wonderful morning?

46
00:06:43,181 --> 00:06:44,614
Just think about it.

47
00:06:46,952 --> 00:06:50,353
We've been through this before.
You'd hate it on Mars.

48
00:06:50,422 --> 00:06:53,255
It's dry, it's ugly, it's boring.

49
00:06:54,326 --> 00:06:58,456
I mean, really, a revolution
could break out there any second.

50
00:06:58,530 --> 00:07:00,464
Cohaagen says
it's just a few extremists.

51
00:07:01,700 --> 00:07:03,133
You believe him?

52
